'''Craster''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 2|second]]Â and [[Season 3|third]] seasons. He is played by guest star [[Robert Pugh]] and debuts in &quot;[[The North Remembers]].&quot; Craster is a member of the Free Folk and an unsavory ally of the [[Night's Watch]].

